0%87%EA%B2%8C-%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%BC%EC%A3%BC%EC%86%8C-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D%EC%9D%84-%ED%95%B4%EC%A3%BC%EC%85%94%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"↑ 이렇게 메일주소 등록을 해주셔야 합니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>↑ 이렇게 메일주소 등록을 해주셔야 합니다!</h3>\n<p>( <del>제 주소로 등록해주시면 감ㅅ…</del> )</p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h3 id=\"참고로\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%EB%A1%9C\" aria-label=\"참고로 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고로!</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">이메일을 등록 하신 후, 처음으로 push 하시는 시점에\n그동안 누락되었던 commit ( push ) 이 갱신되요!</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"-이렇게해도-달라지는게-없다는건-크흠-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%9D%B4%EB%A0%87%EA%B2%8C%ED%95%B4%EB%8F%84-%EB%8B%AC%EB%9D%BC%EC%A7%80%EB%8A%94%EA%B2%8C-%EC%97%86%EB%8B%A4%EB%8A%94%EA%B1%B4-%ED%81%AC%ED%9D%A0-\" aria-label=\" 이렇게해도 달라지는게 없다는건 크흠  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"